{"tid":558124,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"小麗年宵擺檔扭波賣袋","createTime":"2018-02-12T04:02:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-15T01:04:00.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d4899b73b76c551bc4dc4768861768763947b158","tid":558124,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T04:02:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180212/20302900\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180212%2F20302900&d=iwyn6yoGta3D5KB84zi1lJZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=98fb6129\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180212%2F20302900&h=8ed077f0\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180212/20302900</a><br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：<br />\n小麗年宵擺檔扭波賣袋 - 李八方<br />\n<br />\n專欄專論   <br />\n         <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180212/large/12lp2p04.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180212%2Flarge%2F12lp2p04.jpg&h=d96cddf4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n劉小麗學識用氣球扭出大吉同桃花公仔。<br />\n<br />\n被DQ議員資格嘅劉小麗，今年喺維園年宵擺攤，名叫「小麗新春墟市」，第一晚已由朝早10點踩到凌晨3點。小麗特別去上堂扭氣球，𠵱家已經可以扭出大吉同桃花等公仔，佢透露嚟緊情人節仲整埋玫瑰，相信有助銷情。<br />\n<br />\n除咗扭波，小麗更親自為布袋畫咗幅畫，配上「在頹垣中創造希望」八字，希望香港人唔好灰心，繼續創造希望，佢亦同設計師合作，整咗款希臘神話西西弗斯嘅布袋，寓意以堅毅意志，就能夠對抗荒誕嘅打壓。但最好賣嘅係一款寫有「與其儲錢買樓，不如輕鬆遠走」嘅布袋，小麗相信表達到香港人對樓價過高嘅不滿，另一款熱賣布袋就寫有「我要瞓到自然醒」，八方相信係一眾打工仔最貼身嘅願望咯！"},{"pid":"2747bb3fb8388bcaf7be3c714107bdfd9ab8180f","tid":558124,"uid":2429,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T05:59:22.000Z","msg":"殘到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f601f22ae60e755bfd275652e844774cbea97d55","tid":558124,"uid":111253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T06:05:31.000Z","msg":"佢其實有咩撈而家"},{"pid":"ddc5dc5b8ffda7ae9fe263d6efab210e2a4f51ac","tid":558124,"uid":7854,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T06:06:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://viralviralvideos.com/wp-content/uploads/meme/2014/08/Fap-fap-fap-GIF-2015.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fviralviralvideos.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fmeme%2F2014%2F08%2FFap-fap-fap-GIF-2015.gif&h=789ec41e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"88fcd50f454bbb5c5463616a3c8a45ee2abd2f64","tid":558124,"uid":3482,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T15:17:10.000Z","msg":"頭先行維園見到真人其實 ok 喎，<br />\n同佢兩個人流落荒島有得屌一定屌"},{"pid":"1370f1e5d8ccf3d2bf3424beab75c4e036b84bd7","tid":558124,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T16:49:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1c900e32a8708f7744cc284a33697aadaf860df9","tid":558124,"uid":6026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T22:38:50.000Z","msg":"小麗老母新春袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c347dddd5cc695c209da3e08284fdbdf563383c6","tid":558124,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f601f22ae60e755bfd275652e844774cbea97d55","tid":558124,"uid":111253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T06:05:31.000Z","msg":"佢其實有咩撈而家"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T01:04:00.000Z","msg":"收租都夠食過世~佢自住果層都成千萬"}]}